OL,3,CWelfare bill rebellion is 'warning
OL,4,Cshot' to Prime Minister says Welsh MP
OL,6,FA Welsh MP says a planned rebellion of
OL,7,Fmore than a hundred of her Labour
OL,8,Fcolleagues is a "warning shot" to the
OL,9,FPrime Minister to change his approach
OL,10,Fto welfare cuts.
OL,12,F108 Labour MPs have signed what's
OL,13,Fknown as a 'reasoned amendment' that
OL,14,Fcould scupper the UK Government's
OL,15,Fwelfare reform bill when it returns to
OL,16,Fthe Commons on July 1st.
