OL,3,CWelfare bill rebellion is 'warning
OL,4,Cshot' to Prime Minister says Welsh MP
OL,6,FUnder the proposals, the number of
OL,7,Fpeople eligible for Personal
OL,8,FIndependence Payments (PIPs) would be
OL,9,Freduced, saving up to #5bn a year.
OL,10,FMinisters, including the Prime
OL,11,FMinister and the Chancellor Of the
OL,12,FExchequer say reform is vital as is
OL,13,Fcurbing the rapidly-growing benefits
OL,14,Fbill.
OL,16,FThree Welsh Labour MPs are among those
OL,17,Fwho've signed the amendment. They are
OL,18,FSteve Witherden, Henry Tuffnell and
OL,19,FRuth Jones.
