OL,3,CWelfare bill rebellion is 'warning
OL,4,Cshot' to Prime Minister says Welsh MP
OL,6,FThe Newport West and Islwyn MP is also
OL,7,Fthe chair of the cross-party Welsh
OL,8,FAffairs Select Committee.
OL,10,FShe's told ITV Cymru Wales that, while
OL,11,Fhas "absolutely no problems" with the
OL,12,Fprinciples of the UK Government's
OL,13,Fplans, her serious concerns are "over
OL,14,Fthe mechanisms of it (such as ) the
OL,15,Fassessment process: we know that ...
OL,16,F80% of people who appeal, win their
OL,17,Fappeal so therefore the assessment
OL,18,Fprocess is currently flawed. There's
OL,19,Fnothing in the bill about changing
OL,20,Fthat assessment."
