OL,6,FShe went on to say that, "Also, if we
OL,7,Fwant to get people into work, where
OL,8,Fare these jobs that are flexible to
OL,9,Fallow people say with relapsing
OL,10,Fmultiple sclerosis, who can't walk one
OL,11,Fday ... and can't work. Where are
OL,12,Fthose jobs? I haven't seen any
OL,13,Fevidence that those jobs are there
OL,14,Fyet. Access to work is another issue.
OL,16,F"There's lots of talk about and we
OL,17,Fneed to improve things, but the actual
OL,18,Fimprovements won't come in until the
OL,19,Fend of this parliament, whereas the
OL,20,Fcuts are going to start coming next
OL,21,Fyear."
