OL,6,FAsked if he she would drop her
OL,7,Fopposition if her concerns were met,
OL,8,FMs Jones said, "Obviously it is a
OL,9,Fwarning shot and we aren't happy at
OL,10,Fthe moment. We didn't come into this
OL,11,Fplace to disadvantage people with
OL,12,Fdisabilities and it's really important
OL,13,Fthat we are seen to be fair. And I
OL,14,Fthink that's the problem. So I'm very
OL,15,Fhappy to listen, I'm all ears to
OL,16,Flisten to what the government's got as
OL,17,Fa suggestion for the way forward."
