OL,3,CWelfare bill rebellion is 'warning
OL,4,Cshot' to Prime Minister says Welsh MP
OL,6,FHe said that, "It seems there are now
OL,7,Fenough potential Labour rebels to stop
OL,8,Fthe reforms when the welfare reform
OL,9,Fbill is voted on next week, although,
OL,10,Fdespite Wales being hit
OL,11,Fdisproportionately hard, it appears
OL,12,Fthat only a handful of Labour MPs from
OL,13,FWales are on that list of rebels.
OL,15,F"So as the Labour leader in Wales,
OL,16,Fwill she urge her members at
OL,17,FWestminster to rebel to protect
OL,18,Fdisabled people in Wales and guard
OL,19,FWelsh spending. Or will she urge them
OL,20,Fto remain loyal to Keir Starmer?"
