OL,6,FA Number 10 spokesman said: "We will
OL,7,Freform welfare to provide one-to-one
OL,8,Fsupport to help people try work
OL,9,Fsafely, protect people with lifelong
OL,10,Fconditions from endless reassessments
OL,11,Fand increase the basic level of
OL,12,Fsupport for low-income families.
OL,14,F"That means the Government will always
OL,15,Fprotect those who can't work, will
OL,16,Fprovide real opportunity for those who
OL,17,Fcan and will build a welfare system
OL,18,Fthat's fair, strong and there for the
